<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>
<head>
    <title>Download Confirmation Email</title>
    <style>
        html, body {
            font-family: arial, verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        .email__intro,
        .email__info {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .email__first,
        .email__last {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .email__last {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .email__link--download {
            display: block;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class='email'>
    <div class='email__body'>
        <p class='email__intro'>Hello!</p>

        <p class='email__first'>
            Thank you for your interest in {{ product.name }} - I hope you really enjoy using it. I'd love to checkout anything you create with it in the future, so always feel free to share!
        </p>

        <p class='email__info'>
            For reference, your order ID is <span class='order-number'>{{ id }}</span>.
            Please click on the filename below to begin downloading (this URL is accessible for 12 hours). If you have any questions, take a look at the
            <a class='email__link' href='https://mattmaxwell.dev/shop/faq' target='_blank'>
                shop's FAQ page
            </a>
            or feel free to send me an
            <a class='email__link' href='mailto:maxwellmattryan@gmail.com' target='_blank'>
                email
            </a>
            if you just wanna chat!
        </p>

        <a class='email__link email__link--download' href={{ signedUrl }} target='_blank'>
            {{ product.filename }}
        </a>

        <p class='email__last'>Cheers!</p>

        <p class='email__outro'>Sincerely,</p>

        <p class='email__outro'>Matthew</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
